<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>No Account Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 100px;
        }
        .main-content {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .main-content img {
            width: 150px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .main-content h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .main-content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .search-bar {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .search-bar input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .back-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/100x100/?logo" alt="Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="main-content">
            <img src="https://source.unsplash.com/150x150/?error" alt="No Account Found">
            <h1>No Account Found</h1>
            <p>We couldn't find the account you were looking for. It might have been removed or never existed.</p>
        
            <a href="#" class="back-button">Go Back</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? <a href="#">Contact us</a> | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
